name: Do or Die
overview: Here is where you'll witness some of the most deadly situations ever caught on tape and put your survival knowledge to the test. Do you have what it takes to come out alive?

episodes.name: Raging Bull
episodes.overview: Survival knowledge is tested via video footage of deadly scenarios. First up: a rampaging bull; an out-of-control driver; a giant wave.

episodes.name: Disaster in the Sky
episodes.overview: A skydiving accident, a burning car with a man trapped beneath it, and an aggravated octopus assault are featured.

episodes.name: Choking to Death
episodes.overview: Methods for saving a choking victim are featured.

episodes.name: Killer Tsunami!
episodes.overview: Options for surviving a tsunami are proposed.

episodes.name: Deadly Rapids
episodes.overview: A kayaker in perilous waters; a driver trapped by wildfire; and a single-engine plane stymied by unusual weather.

episodes.name: Shark Attack!
episodes.overview: A shark attacks a caged diver; a snowmobile driver races from a deadly avalanche; and a deadly reptile forces a showdown.

episodes.name: Up in Flames
episodes.overview: An angry elephant attacks a car; an incidental spark sets a person on fire at a gas station; a snowmobile balances on the edge of a cliff.

episodes.name: A Gory End
episodes.overview: A massive earthquake devastates an office building; raging bulls try to gore participants in the Running of the Bulls; a person attempts to keep afloat while being washed down the Los Angeles River.

episodes.name: Falling Through Ice
episodes.overview: A fatal dip into freezing water; a showdown with a pack of dogs; a collision between boats.

episodes.name: Disaster on the High Seas
episodes.overview: A seal attacks a swimmer; a yacht crashes into another boat; a jeep tumbles down a jagged slope.

episodes.name: Icy Highway Crisis
episodes.overview: A tractor trailer slides on black ice; an alligator snaps at a person; an escalator's brakes malfunction.

episodes.name: Deadly Ocean Pull
episodes.overview: A swimmer tries to escape a strong current; a tenant dangles out the window of a burning apartment building; a person dodges an oncoming train by diving between the tracks.

episodes.name: Fire in the Sky
episodes.overview: A meteor explosion; a building collapse; an anaconda strike.

episodes.name: Terrible Twister
episodes.overview: A tornado spins down a road toward oncoming cars; a large wave crashes down on a surfer; a dirt biker attempts a dangerously long jump.

episodes.name: Antler Assault
episodes.overview: A wild deer attacks; a giant wave engulfs a boat after a glacier breaks apart; a misjudged bike jump leads to a 80-foot plummet.

episodes.name: Deadly Mudslide
episodes.overview: Included: an uncontrolled rush of shoppers; a dog attack; a mudslide.
